high_descs: Turn around, go straight to the green table.
Take the large knife from the table.
Turn left, go to the oven ahead.
Put the knife in the left pot on the stove top.
Take the left pot from the stove top.
Turn around, go straight, turn left at the green table.
Put the pot on the left side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a green knife in it on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and stand in front of the counter with the knife on it.
Pick the knife up from the counter.
Go left and stand in front of the stove.
Put the knife in the pot on the left side of the stove.
Pick the pot up from the left side of the stove.
Turn around and stand in front of the table.
Put the pot down on the table in front of the bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a knife in it on the table.

high_descs: Turn around to go to the table behind you.
Pick up the knife on the table, behind the pen.
Turn around, then turn right to go to the stove.
Put the knife in the left most pot.
Pick up the left most pot on the stove.
Turn around, go forward, then turn left to approach the table.
Place the pot with the knife in it on the table, in front of the wine bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in a pot on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and approach the table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Turn left and walk to the stove.
Put the knife in the pan on the front left burner.
Pick up the Pan on the stove with the knife in it.
Turn around, walk halfway across the room, then turn left and face the table.
Place the pan on the table.
anns.task_desc: To put a knife plus a pan on the table.
